HEADWORD: Endurant
<hw>En*dur"ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable of enduring
fatigue, pain, hunger, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The ibex is a remarkably <qex>endurant</qex> animal.</q>
<rj><qau>J. G. Wood.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Endure</ent>⟦br⟧
